You can exclude transitive dependencies from being imported:
```
implementation &quot;my-dependency-1:module:1.0.0&quot;
implementation (&quot;my-dependency-2:module:1.0.0&quot;) {
  exclude group: &quot;group&quot;, module: &quot;module&quot;
}
```
While the transitive dependency would be imported with `my-dependency-1`, it would be excluded from `my-dependency-2`.

